text: The iPhone 14 and iPhone 14 Plus are smartphones developed and made by Apple Inc. They are the sixteenth generation of the iPhone. It succeeds the iPhone 13 and iPhone 13 Mini. It was announced on September 7, 2022 at 2022 Apple Worldwide Developers Conference and were announced in Apple Event. The iPhone 14 was released on September 16, 2022, whilst the iPhone 14 Plus was released on October 7, 2022. It is the first iPhone to use the Plus title since iPhone 8 Plus in 2017. On February 2025, iPhone 14 was no longer available when iPhone 16e came out. == References == == Related pages == * iPhone 13 * iPhone 13 Pro * Apple Inc. == Other websites == * Category:Mobile phones introduced in 2022 Category:IPhone
